{{also|yellow-brick road}}

==English==

===Etymology===
From the classic film ''The Wizard of Oz'' and the book series on which it was based. Originally the literal road to the [[w:Emerald City|Emerald City]], which was paved with yellow bricks possibly to invoke the notion of [[gold]].

